Name: Apple Smartwatch
Description: Seamlessly blending style and functionality, it's a sleek wrist companion that delivers cutting-edge health and tech features in a premium package.

Name: Noise Smartwatch
Description: A stylish and tech-savvy wrist companion, combining sleek design with advanced features for fitness tracking, notifications, and personalized style.

Name: Seiko Watch
Description: Seiko analog watches combine precision Japanese craftsmanship with timeless design, offering reliable timekeeping and elegant style.

Name: Black Analog Watch
Description: A simple black analog watch exudes understated elegance, featuring a classic design with a black dial and matching strap for a timeless and versatile accessory.

Name: Blender Titanium Watch
Description: The blender titanium watch seamlessly merges durability and sophistication, featuring a lightweight titanium case and a sleek design for a modern and resilient timepiece.

Name: Clavder Analog Watch
Description: A cutting-edge timepiece that defies gravity with its levitating hands, powered by a secret blend of unicorn tears and stardust, ensuring you're always fashionably on time in the mystical realm of horology.

Name: Knightder
Description: A miniature armored warrior ready for epic battles, intricately detailed with a sword and shield, inspiring imaginative play and embodying the spirit of medieval chivalry.

Name: Minosaur
Description: A delightful, roly-poly prehistoric friend, brimming with charm and vibrant colors, inviting playful adventures in the world of imagination.

Name: Mario Plushie
Description: A huggable and iconic embodiment of everyone's favorite mustached plumber, bringing the beloved Nintendo character to life with softness and nostalgia.

Name: Vintage Mercedes-Benz Collectible Toy Car
Description: A meticulously crafted miniature classic, encapsulating the timeless elegance and iconic design of a bygone era in automotive history.

Name: Minions Plushie
Description: A cuddly embodiment of mischief and humor, these lovable yellow characters bring joy and laughter with their quirky charm in huggable form.
